===制作组解散以及3D Realms裁员－2009年5月 ===

<!-- If changing this header, please also update the Subsection Wikilink in the "Release" section of the infobox. -->

3D Realms于2009年5月8日暂停本作的制作组活动，原因是资金不足，但知情人反映仍有一个小规模的团队继续本作的开发。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://forums.3drealms.com/vb/showthread.php?t=35716 |title=3DR "smaller studio now," "will continue to operate as a company" |publisher=Forums.3drealms.com |date=2009-05-18 |accessdate=2009-07-21 |archive-date=2021-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126143807/http://forums.3drealms.com/vb/showthread.php?t=35716 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="official_release">{{cite web | url = http://kotaku.com/5259942/3d-realms-were-not-closing-spent-20-million-on-duke-nukem-forever | title = 3D Realms: We're Not Closing, Spent $20 Million On Duke Nukem Forever | first = Stephen | last = Totilo | date = 2009-05-18 | accessdate = 2009-05-18 | publisher = [[Kotaku|Kotaku]] | archive-date = 2009-05-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090521113851/http://kotaku.com/5259942/3d-realms-were-not-closing-spent-20-million-on-duke-nukem-forever | dead-url = no }}</ref>《永远的毁灭公爵》的开发工作停顿，结局不明。作为发行商的Take-Two Interactive回应道他们仍旧掌握有本作的发行权，但已经停止为本作拨款。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/technology/8037688.stm |title=Technology | Duke Nukem developer goes bust |publisher=BBC News |date=2009-05-07 |accessdate=2009-07-21 |archive-date=2009-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090629035213/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/technology/8037688.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

同年5月7日到5月8日，一名自称是制作组前雇员的人上传了一批本作的截图、概念图、模型设定以及告别信息。5月9，10，11，12日也发生了类似的信息泄漏。<ref name="misc_link_1">{{cite web | url = http://talkinrealatyou.blogspot.com/ | title = http://talkinrealatyou.blogspot.com/ | publisher = ''Unknown'' | access-date = 2009-07-27 | archive-date = 2020-12-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201210034941/http://talkinrealatyou.blogspot.com/ | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="misc_link_2">{{cite web | url = http://www.squidcakes.blogspot.com/ | title = http://www.squidcakes.blogspot.com/ | publisher = ''Unknown'' | access-date = 2009-07-27 | archive-date = 2020-12-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201210034943/http://squidcakes.blogspot.com/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>5月9日，Duke4.net论坛上流出一段非官方《永远的毁灭公爵》游戏视频。放出视频的用户称，该视频由一位在本作制作组中工作的动画设计师Bryan Brewer用作个人展示，视频泄漏时Brewer还在等待布罗撒批准他使用这段视频。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://forums.duke4.net/index.php?showtopic=814 |title=Duke Nukem Forever Media |publisher=Duke4.net |date= |accessdate=2009-07-21 |archive-date=2010-06-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100625232902/http://forums.duke4.net/index.php?showtopic=814 |dead-url=no }}</ref>2009年5月10日另一段游戏动画视频被漏出，同一Duke4.net论坛用户此后还陆续泄漏了28张游戏截图和本一些介绍本作剧情的文档。这些截图是从一位Linkedin雇员Richard Huenink的文档中取得的。

此后，[[G4TV|G4TV]]和[[IGN|IGN]]等媒体开始怀疑3D Realms解散制作组是否一次商业炒作。<ref>{{cite web |author=Posted May 12, 2009 - By Stephen Johnson |url=http://g4tv.com/thefeed/blog/post/695479/Is-The-Duke-Nukem-Forever-Cancellation-A-Huge-Publicity-Stunt.html |title=Is The 'Duke Nukem Forever' Cancellation A Huge Publicity Stunt? |publisher=G4tv.com |date=2009-05-12 |accessdate=2009-07-21 |archive-date=2012-08-11 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69q6lbtAp?url=http://www.g4tv.com/thefeed/blog/post/695479/is-the-duke-nukem-forever-cancellation-a-huge-publicity-stunt/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://ve3d.ign.com/articles/news/47009/Saved-Duke-Nukem-Dot-Com |title=Saved Duke Nukem Dot Com? |publisher=Ve3d.ign.com |date= |accessdate=2009-07-21 |archive-date=2012-08-11 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69q6nQLWg?url=http://ve3d.ign.com/articles/news/47009/Saved-Duke-Nukem-Dot-Com |dead-url=no }}</ref>但是在2009年5月18日3D Realms正式证实了本作制作组被解散的事实。<ref name="official_release" />

2009年5月14日，Take-Two以未能按期完成《永远的毁灭公爵》为由起诉3D Realms——诉讼中使用了后者的注册公司名：'''Apogee Software Ltd'''。Take-Two诉称，他们在2000年仅为从[[Infogrames|Infogrames]]处购得本作的发行权就支付了1200万美元。<ref name="Take-Two Sues Duke Nukem Forever Devs Over Failure To Deliver"/>3D Realms则辩称他们并未收到那些钱，该协议只在Infogrames与Take-Two两公司之间有效，与被告无关。<ref name="3D Realms' 米勒 responds to Take-Two Nukem Suit".>[http://kotaku.com/5257517/3d-realms-米勒-responds-to-take+two-nukem-suit 3D Realms' 米勒 responds to Take-Two Nukem Suit]. Kotaku. Retrieved May 16, 2009.</ref>这次诉讼看上去是一次合同纠纷，但上述1200万美元并非争议重点。<ref name="lawsuit">{{cite web | url = http://www.shacknews.com/onearticle.x/58642 | title = Take-Two Sues 3D Realms for Failing to Deliver Duke Nukem Forever (Updated) | first = Nick | last = Breckon | date = 2009-05-14 | accessdate = 2009-05-16 | publisher = [[Shacknews|Shacknews]] | archive-date = 2009-05-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090516154730/http://www.shacknews.com/onearticle.x/58642 | dead-url = no }}</ref>Take-Two向法院申请针对3D Realms的禁制令及诉前财产保全，防止后者在诉讼过程中蓄意破坏游戏。<ref name="lawsuit2">{{cite web | url = http://www.shacknews.com/onearticle.x/58651 | title = Take-Two v. 3D Realms Court Documents Materialize, 3DR's 斯科特·米勒 Responds | first = Nick | last = Breckon | date = 2009-05-15 | accessdate = 2009-05-16 | publisher = [[Shacknews|Shacknews]] | archive-date = 2009-05-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090518092202/http://www.shacknews.com/onearticle.x/58651 | dead-url = no }}</ref>The court denied Take-Two's request for a temporary restraining order.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.shacknews.com/docs/press/20090518_dnf_3dr_.x |title=http://www.shacknews.com/docs/press/20090518_dnf_3dr_.x |publisher=Shacknews |date=2009-05-18 |accessdate=2009-07-21 |archive-date=2010-07-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100730214023/http://www.shacknews.com/docs/press/20090518_dnf_3dr_.x |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://ve3d.ign.com/articles/news/48496/3DR-Spent-20m-On-DNF-Denies-Allegations-Reveals-New-Duke-Game |title=3DR Spent $20m On DNF; Denies Allegations; Reveals New Duke Game |publisher=Ve3d.ign.com |date= |accessdate=2009-07-21 |archive-date=2009-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090626070819/http://ve3d.ign.com/articles/news/48496/3DR-Spent-20m-On-DNF-Denies-Allegations-Reveals-New-Duke-Game |dead-url=no }}</ref>

随着诉讼文书的公开，证实早在2007年[[2K_Games|2K Games]]就开始设计一款使用毁灭公爵系列世界观的游戏，代号"Duke Begins"，预计2010年中完成。关于《永远的毁灭公爵》开发工作于2009年4月在未得Apogee同意的情况下强行中止，Apogee抗辩称那是“Take-Two和2K Games试图胁迫Apogee将毁灭公爵系列相关权益以不公平的低价转让”。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamepolitics.com/2009/06/22/court-filing-2kgames-developing-quotduke-beginsquot |title=Court Filing: 2KGames Developing "Duke Begins" |publisher=GamePolitics |date= |accessdate=2009-07-21 |archive-date=2021-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413020406/http://www.gamepolitics.com/2009/06/22/court-filing-2kgames-developing-quotduke-beginsquot |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamersdailynews.com/story-12037-Apogee-Files-CounterSuit-Against-Take-Two.html |title=GDN: Apogee Files Counter-Suit Against Take Two |publisher=Gamersdailynews.com |date=2009-06-22 |accessdate=2009-07-21 |archive-date=2009-10-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091011084758/http://www.gamersdailynews.com/story-12037-Apogee-Files-CounterSuit-Against-Take-Two.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

2009年7月下旬，斯科特·米勒在他的[[Facebook|Facebook]]页面上声明：“如果你还不知道，‘公爵’只是小憩片刻，马上就会回到游戏”。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://sknr.net/2009/07/08/duke-nukem-may-be-back/ |title=Duke Nukem May Be Back!!!! |publisher=Sknr.net |date=2009-07-08 |accessdate=2009-07-21 |archive-date=2012-08-11 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69q7eUnpM?url=http://sknr.net/2009/07/08/duke-nukem-may-be-back/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>不久便证实在Facebook有毁灭公爵的官方页面被创建，在那里《永远的毁灭公爵》截图被不断公开，包括Cycloid Emperor和其他Battlelord的图像。7月17日，该页面因违反Facebook不允许虚构角色创建页面的规定而被关闭。当天斯科特·米勒宣称新的官方页面一星期内就会上线，一张截图赶在毁灭公爵Facebook页面被关闭前上传至该网站，图片表现了游戏中一位脱衣舞女的背影。

7月20日斯科特·米勒说他并不急着建设官方页面，该网站也许会在一两个月内上线。“何况，在网站上线前我们必须给它准备一些爆炸性新闻”。

在3D Realms被关闭的消息证明是虚假的后，Jace Hall又在Jace Hall Show本季最后一集中收入了两分钟的《永远的毁灭公爵》游戏画面。

===復活===

在2010年9月的Penny Arcade展覽中，[[Gearbox_Software|Gearbox Software]]正式公佈他們承接了[[3D_Realms|3D Realms]]的進度繼續開發《永远的毁灭公爵》。其中一名開發者更於訪問中表示遊戲將於2011年內發行上市。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ustream.tv/channel-popup/games---2k |title=存档副本 |access-date=2010-09-04 |archive-date=2011-10-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111007194739/http://www.ustream.tv/channel-popup/games---2k |dead-url=no }}</ref>

Gearbox的總裁Randy Pitchford表示他們早於2009年已經開始接手永远的毁灭公爵，而他們現在亦擁有[[毁灭公爵|毁灭公爵]]系列的版權。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2010/09/03/duke-nukem-forever-hitting-in-2011.aspx |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2010-09-04 |archive-date=2010-09-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100909104949/http://gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2010/09/03/duke-nukem-forever-hitting-in-2011.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==發售==

2011年5月10日：正當玩家議論《永遠的毀滅公爵》是否再次跳票時，《永遠的毀滅公爵》在Steam建立了[http://store.steampowered.com/app/57900/ 商店頁面] {{Wayback|url=http://store.steampowered.com/app/57900/ |date=20210211072829 }}，在頁面裡明確說明了該遊戲在2011年6月10日發售，並且已經可以在steam預購（確定於6月10日解鎖）。

2011年6月9日，《永远的毁灭公爵》PC正式版开始在Steam接受付费下载，14年跳票史就此终结。

